{"tid":2002290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實「光復香港，時代革命」係咩意思？","createTime":"2020-05-05T06:08:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T10:59:19.000Z","uid":321421,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1aee9b09167ac315bc4730a12444603b0da81519","tid":2002290,"uid":321421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:08:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">到底句口號係咩意思？</span></span><br />\n「光復」，就是「恢復故國」、「收復失土」的意思。最常見的說法是：香港在1997年回歸中國時「淪陷」了、成為了被佔領的地方。「光復香港」，就是要從中國手上「奪回香港」，復歸港英殖民時期港人據說擁有主權的狀況，或宣稱只有脫離中國、才可以恢復港人在1997年前擁有過的自由。<br />\n<br />\n時代不分年齡，就算年紀大的，只要相信自由、擁抱自由，你就是新時代；就算年紀輕的，思維都是舊的、擺脫不了舊框架，就是舊時代的人。<br />\n<br />\n他們的「新時代」，其實就是「新的殖民時代」；他們的「自由」，是指不受約束地反共反大陸、乃至脫離中共統治的狀態；他們的「革命」，就是要通過暴力實現他們的殖民主義「理想」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>總言之，「光復香港，時代革命」的思想和政治內核，就是只要能夠脫離中國/中共，即使成為被西方奴役的殖民地也在所不辭。這場「革命」的「戰旗」是港英旗、米字旗和星條旗的事實本身，就鮮明地展現了最前線青年們為香港設定的願景。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「光復香港，時代革命」本來就係爭取香港獨立嘅口號</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://international-online.org/2019/07/31/restorehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finternational-online.org%2F2019%2F07%2F31%2Frestorehk%2F&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktX4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=ab17f2cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://international-online.org/2019/07/31/restorehk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港邊有條件獨立？</span></span><br />\n我係黃㗎，但香港真係有條件獨立咩？<br />\n香港民族黨2016年嘅一本小冊子答到你。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">[香港獨立的條件]</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/hknationalparty/posts/524196607779298\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fhknationalparty%2Fposts%2F524196607779298&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktX4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=55f97906\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/hknationalparty/posts/524196607779298</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">香港獨立 唯一出路</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"1f017f0c78e5412a2c26e70fcdaacefa91930116","tid":2002290,"uid":41944,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:09:53.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 唯一出路!!!"},{"pid":"fa0d6a92cf8e9544a688bd1e46590b573166deaa","tid":2002290,"uid":321421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f017f0c78e5412a2c26e70fcdaacefa91930116","tid":2002290,"uid":41944,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:09:53.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 唯一出路!!!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:10:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d192290aea5eef4b2d95f9b8fa2a66faeb27e49","tid":2002290,"uid":136431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:12:13.000Z","msg":"光復香港人嘅香港<br />\n恢復香港人嘅主權"},{"pid":"aad3aaf2c179b9fc56972415c6d4e7230b4a4402","tid":2002290,"uid":321421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d192290aea5eef4b2d95f9b8fa2a66faeb27e49","tid":2002290,"uid":136431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:12:13.000Z","msg":"光復香港人嘅香港<br />\n恢復香港人嘅主權"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:13:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe453ec2f4424b5d1ac202fd0898f693575ac7f5","tid":2002290,"uid":300785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:14:04.000Z","msg":"D識呢句野嘅癈老就話香港未死  光復條撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6405edb403e504b2af419aa31f18ba90bab000","tid":2002290,"uid":136431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:15:01.000Z","msg":"